README

1/ create new angular project
>ng new ang6-httpclient
I don tthink angular likes hyphens


2/start project
>ng serve

3/ start on a given host or port:
>ng serve --host 0.0.0.0 --port 3000


4/ generate service:
ng generate service <name of service>
ng g service rest

5/ generate component:
ng generate component <name of component>
ng g component product
ng g component product-add
